        public GeneratorSetting(java.lang.String name,
                        int numberOfChars,
                        boolean upperCaseSelected,
                        boolean lowerCaseSelected,
                        boolean digitsSelected,
                        boolean specialCharactersSelected,
                        boolean ownCharactersSelected,
                        java.lang.String ownCharactersText)
        Constructs a setting using the specified settings.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the generator setting.
        numberOfChars - the number of characters.
        upperCaseSelected - whether uppercase characters should be used.
        lowerCaseSelected - whether lowercase characters should be used.
        digitsSelected - whether digits should be used.
        specialCharactersSelected - whether special characters should be used.
        ownCharactersSelected - whether own characters should be used.
        ownCharactersText - own characters.
